To build/deploy LingvoMovie Project:
0) Install latest Oracle JDK
1) Install latest WildFly app. server
2) Install MySql
3) Install MongoDB
4) Export variables specified in lingvo-movie.sh
5) Start WildFly
6) Run mvn clean install -P first-build
7) Create DataSource with JNDI name = java:/jdbc/LearningEnglish in WildFly pointing to some schema in MySql
8) Run mvn clean deploy